   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Just a reminder:\r\n\r\n[Translation Strings Policy](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/translation_strings_policy.md#do-not-translate-internal-errors):\r\n> Do not translate internal errors, log messages, or messages that appear on the RPC interface. If an error is to be shown to the user, use a translatable generic message, then log the detailed message to the log. E.g., \"A fatal internal error occurred, see debug.log for details\". This helps troubleshooting; if the error is the same for everyone, the likelihood is increased that it can be found using a search engine.",
